textAfterTable: Highlights: An elegant ship with over $2 million worth of art including paintings, armor and Jacob's Staircase, a sculpture of Murano stained glass. Formal dining in the two-tier Rotterdam Dining room, or relaxed ambiance for all three meals can be found in the Lido Restaurant. The Wajang Theatre shows two movies daily and also hosts culinary demonstrations on specific sailings. Past guest of the Veendam rave about the attentive staff that go above and beyond the expected. Your Package Includes: Your package includes shipboard accommodations, ocean transportation, fabulous entertainment and daily activities, on-board meals and some beverages.
